!!>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
!! NEMO/OPA  Configuration namelist : used to overwrite defaults values defined in SHARED/namelist_ref
